<template lang="pug">
    div.ymap-container
        yandexMap(@click="onClick" :coords="coords" :zoom="10")
        ymapMarker(:coords="coords" marker-id="123" hint-content="some hint")
</template>

<script>
import { yandexMap, ymapMarker } from 'vue-yandex-maps'
export default {
  name: 'Map',
  data: () => ({
    coords: [
      54.82896654088406,
      39.831893822753904
    ]
  }),
  methods: {
    onClick (e) {
      this.coords = e.get('coords')
    }
  },
  computed: {
  },
  components: {
    yandexMap,
    ymapMarker
  }
}
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
.ymap-container {
  height: 100%;
}
</style>
